<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to NEXST Starter Kit</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      color: #374151;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #000000;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 32px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px;
    }
    .content h2 {
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #000000;
    }
    .content p {
      margin: 0 0 24px 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #4b5563;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      background-color: #000000;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #1f2937;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 32px 40px;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #000000;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .divider {
      margin: 32px 0;
      border: 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .feature-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .feature-list li {
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #374151;
    }
    .feature-list li:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .feature-list li::before {
      content: "âœ“";
      display: inline-block;
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      margin-right: 12px;
      background-color: #000000;
      color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 50%;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>NEXST Starter Kit</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Welcome, {{firstName}}!</h2>
      <p>Your account has been successfully created and verified. You're now ready to explore all the features of NEXST Starter Kit.</p>

      <p style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
        <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
      </p>

      <hr class="divider">

      <h3 style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #000000;">What's included:</h3>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Secure authentication with email/password and OAuth</li>
        <li>Two-factor authentication for enhanced security</li>
        <li>Session management across multiple devices</li>
        <li>Profile customization and settings</li>
        <li>Real-time notifications and updates</li>
      </ul>

      <hr class="divider">

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
        Need help getting started? Check out our documentation or contact our support team.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent to <strong>{{email}}</strong></p>
      <p>&copy; 2026 NEXST Starter Kit. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
